## 📊 IngredientInventory

### Purpose
Track ingredient levels and check if a coffee can be made.

### Attributes

| Attribute | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `_inventory` | Dict[Ingredient, int] | Current levels |

### Methods

| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `get_quantity(ingredient)` | Get current level |
| `add_ingredient(ingredient, qty)` | Refill (admin) |
| `use_ingredient(ingredient, qty)` | Deduct when making coffee |
| `has_enough_for(recipe)` | Check if all ingredients available |

### Key Decision: Centralized Inventory
- Single `IngredientInventory` instance in the machine
- All coffees and decorators check against same inventory
- Prevents "Latte available" but actually no milk scenario

