## 🏭 CoffeeVendingMachine (Singleton)

### Purpose
Main orchestrator that ties everything together.

### Attributes

| Attribute | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `_instance` | Class variable | Singleton instance |
| `current_state` | MachineState | Current state object |
| `inventory` | IngredientInventory | Ingredient levels |
| `selected_coffee` | Coffee | Currently selected coffee |
| `inserted_amount` | int | Money inserted so far |
| `available_coffees` | List[Coffee] | Menu items |

### Methods

| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `select_coffee(coffee_type)` | Delegate to current state |
| `insert_coin(coin)` | Delegate to current state |
| `dispense()` | Delegate to current state |
| `cancel()` | Delegate to current state |
| `set_state(state)` | Change current state |
| `reset()` | Clear selection, reset amount |

### Key Decision: Singleton
- Only ONE machine instance
- State is shared across all operations
- If asked about multiple machines: "Add a VendingMachineManager"

