## 📝 Design Decisions Summary

| Decision | Choice | Reasoning |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| Payment | Exact amount only | Simplifies design, no change dispenser |
| Customization | Decorator Pattern | Clean way to add extras without modifying base classes |
| Machine states | State Pattern | Clear transitions, each state handles its own logic |
| Coffee types | Class hierarchy | Could use enum + data, but classes allow recipe encapsulation |
| Inventory | Centralized | Single source of truth for all ingredients |
| Cash Box | Not needed | Exact payment, no change tracking |

