## 🧪 Implementation Order

| Step | What | Why |
|------|------|-----|
| 1 | Enums (Ingredient, Coin) | No dependencies |
| 2 | Coffee (abstract) | Base for decorators |
| 3 | Espresso, Latte, Cappuccino | Concrete coffees |
| 4 | CoffeeDecorator (abstract) | Decorator base |
| 5 | SugarDecorator, MilkDecorator | Concrete decorators |
| 6 | IngredientInventory | Needed by machine |
| 7 | MachineState (abstract) | State pattern base |
| 8 | IdleState, AwaitingPaymentState, DispensingState | Concrete states |
| 9 | CoffeeVendingMachine (Singleton) | Ties everything together |
| 10 | Demo | Prove it works |

